WEBVTT

00:08.651 --> 00:10.488
Oh. Here's one.

00:16.369 --> 00:17.618
It says "compact."

00:17.738 --> 00:19.553
This is compact.

00:23.009 --> 00:24.404
Compact, huh?

00:24.438 --> 00:26.531
Relax. We'll use
the back door.

00:26.651 --> 00:28.297
What back door?

00:28.331 --> 00:30.378
Where is it? I can't--

00:30.413 --> 00:32.317
It's right there!

00:32.353 --> 00:35.290
[Groaning and grunting]

00:35.324 --> 00:38.092
[Groaning and grunting]

00:38.897 --> 00:41.200
Ooh. I got to oil that.

00:41.235 --> 00:52.410
